# PERSONAL

IMAPAccount personal
Host imaps.example.com
Port 993
User user@example.com
# Pass ***
PassCmd "gpg --decrypt ~/.passwords/user@example.com.gpg 2> /dev/null"
SSLType IMAPS
# CertificateFile /path/to/file

IMAPStore personal-remote
Account personal

MaildirStore personal-local
SubFolders Verbatim
PATH ~/.mail/personal/
Inbox ~/.mail/personal/Inbox/

Channel personal
Far :personal-remote:
Near :personal-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All

# DEV

IMAPAccount dev
Host imaps.example.com
Port 993
User other.user@example.com
# Pass ***
PassCmd "gpg --decrypt ~/.passwords/other.user@example.com.gpg 2> /dev/null"
SSLType IMAPS
# CertificateFile /path/to/file

IMAPStore dev-remote
Account dev

MaildirStore dev-local
SubFolders Verbatim
PATH ~/.mail/dev/
Inbox ~/.mail/dev/Inbox/

Channel dev
Far :dev-remote:
Near :dev-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Patterns *
CopyArrivalDate yes
Sync All
